        "TileImage": "$($repository d1318c3f-857a-48de-bf4b-6654f95531bd).Image",
        "Description": "Welcome back to Hokkaido 47, The reason we are back here is something is that we forgot to deal. The Devil Tokens cult had few people that partner up with. There&#39;s three people currently here to check what happened to the cult. Dwyer G. Pitt is the leader of this small group with his two brothers. One of the brothers is a drug addict and apparently is on the edge with life after messed up post he did online and has lost everything. Other brother is smart and as we speak trying to figure out who caused the damage of the cult. After that cult contract the facility has gone to major lockdown that no one at the moment can&#39;t leave and enter so i would recommend using Snowmobile on your way out after killing the group. We are aware there&#39;s other partners out there and will likely takeover there spot so we will find out other partners as we speak. I will leave you to prepare. Good Luck.\r\n\r\nExit: Snowmobile",
